---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog – Local SEO Tips for Small Businesses | Rootss Digital
description: Free local SEO tips, Google Business Profile guides, and digital marketing advice for small and family-owned businesses in Visalia CA. Available in English and Spanish.
keywords: local SEO blog Visalia CA, Google Business Profile tips, small business digital marketing blog, bilingual marketing blog Central Valley
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="blog-hero" aria-labelledby="blog-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label" style="color: var(--aqua);">
      <span class="lang-en">Free Education</span>
      <span class="lang-es" hidden>Educación Gratuita</span>
    </p>
    <h1 id="blog-heading">
      <span class="lang-en">Real tips for real business owners</span>
      <span class="lang-es" hidden>Consejos reales para dueños de negocios reales</span>
    </h1>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">No fluff. No jargon. Specific steps you can take today to get your business found in Visalia and beyond.</span>
      <span class="lang-es" hidden>Sin relleno. Sin jerga. Pasos específicos que puedes tomar hoy para que tu negocio sea encontrado en Visalia y más allá.</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="blog-listing" aria-labelledby="posts-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="posts-heading" class="visually-hidden">All Blog Posts</h2>

    {% if collections.posts.length > 0 %}
    <div class="blog-listing-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="blog-listing-card fade-in" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting">
        <div class="blog-card-inner">
          <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">
            <span class="lang-en">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
            <span class="lang-es" hidden>{{ post.date | readableDateEs }}</span>
          </time>
          <h2 itemprop="headline">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" itemprop="url">
              <span class="lang-en">{{ post.data.title }}</span>
              <span class="lang-es" hidden>{{ post.data.titleEs if post.data.titleEs else post.data.title }}</span>
            </a>
          </h2>
          <p itemprop="description">
            <span class="lang-en">{{ post.data.description }}</span>
            <span class="lang-es" hidden>{{ post.data.descriptionEs if post.data.descriptionEs else post.data.description }}</span>
          </p>
          {% if post.data.tags %}
          <div class="post-tags" aria-label="Categories">
            {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
              {% if tag != "posts" %}
              <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          {% endif %}
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-link" itemprop="url">
            <span class="lang-en">Read Post →</span>
            <span class="lang-es" hidden>Leer Artículo →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="text-center" style="padding: 3rem 0;">
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gray);">
        <span class="lang-en">Blog posts are coming soon. Check back shortly.</span>
        <span class="lang-es" hidden>Los artículos del blog llegarán pronto. Vuelve pronto.</span>
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline mt-3">
        <span class="lang-en">Get notified when we post</span>
        <span class="lang-es" hidden>Recibe notificaciones cuando publiquemos</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-banner" aria-label="Free audit CTA">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2>
      <span class="lang-en">Learn faster with a free profile check</span>
      <span class="lang-es" hidden>Aprende más rápido con una revisión de perfil gratis</span>
    </h2>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">Reading is great. Knowing exactly what's wrong with YOUR profile is better.</span>
      <span class="lang-es" hidden>Leer es genial. Saber exactamente qué está mal con TU perfil es mejor.</span>
    </p>
    <a href="/book/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
      <span class="lang-en">Book Your Free Call</span>
      <span class="lang-es" hidden>Reserva Tu Llamada Gratis</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
